Package app.GUI

Class ArrGUI

java.lang.Object
javafx.scene.Node
javafx.scene.Parent
javafx.scene.Group
app.GUI.ArrGUI
All Implemented Interfaces:
javafx.css.Styleable, javafx.event.EventTarget
public class ArrGUI extends javafx.scene.Group
ArrGUI.java Child object of Line Contains an amount of properties relative to the graphical representation of the arrow itself, such as the graphical arrow connecting the two object nodes, it also contains methods for the trigonometrical computations that allow this arrow to stay on the borders of the objects nodes
Since:
17/05/2021
Author:
Dario Loi
See Also:
